<style>
.info-page { padding: 10rem 4rem 8rem; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
.info-page h1 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.info-page h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--warm); }
.info-page .intro { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.9; max-width: 540px; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
.info-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
.info-card { background: #0d0c0a; padding: 2.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
.info-card-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--warm); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; display: block; }
.info-card h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.info-card p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.9; }
.info-card strong { color: var(--paper); font-weight: 400; }
.info-section { margin-bottom: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
.info-section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.info-section h2 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.info-section h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--warm); }
.info-section p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
.info-table th { font-family: 'Syncopate', sans-serif; font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; color: var(--warm); text-transform: uppercase; text-align: left; padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
.info-table td { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
.info-table td:first-child { color: var(--paper); }
</style>

<div class="info-page">
  <div class="reveal">
    <span class="section-label">Delivery</span>
    <h1>Shipping <em>Information</em></h1>
    <p class="intro">We ship to over 50 countries worldwide. All orders are processed within 1–2 business days and shipped from our fulfilment centre in Los Angeles, California.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="info-cards reveal">
    <div class="info-card">
      <span class="info-card-icon">◈</span>
      <h3>Standard</h3>
      <p><strong>5–7 business days</strong><br>Free on orders over $150. $8 flat rate below.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <span class="info-card-icon">◇</span>
      <h3>Express</h3>
      <p><strong>2–3 business days</strong><br>$18 flat rate. Available at checkout.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <span class="info-card-icon">◈</span>
      <h3>Overnight</h3>
      <p><strong>Next business day</strong><br>$35 flat rate. Order by 12pm PST.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section reveal">
    <h2>Domestic <em>Shipping</em></h2>
    <p>All US orders are shipped via UPS or USPS depending on your selected shipping method. Tracking information will be emailed to you once your order has shipped.</p>
    <table class="info-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Method</th>
          <th>Estimated Delivery</th>
          <th>Cost</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Standard Shipping</td><td>5–7 business days</td><td>Free over $150 / $8 below</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Express Shipping</td><td>2–3 business days</td><td>$18</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Overnight Shipping</td><td>Next business day</td><td>$35</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section reveal">
    <h2>International <em>Shipping</em></h2>
    <p>We ship to over 50 countries. International orders are shipped via DHL Express. Delivery times and rates vary by destination. Duties and taxes may apply and are the responsibility of the customer.</p>
    <table class="info-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Region</th>
          <th>Estimated Delivery</th>
          <th>Cost</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Canada & Mexico</td><td>5–8 business days</td><td>$20</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Europe</td><td>7–10 business days</td><td>$30</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Australia & NZ</td><td>8–12 business days</td><td>$35</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rest of World</td><td>10–14 business days</td><td>$40</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="info-section reveal">
    <h2>Order <em>Tracking</em></h2>
    <p>Once your order ships you'll receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. You can track your package directly on the carrier's website or through your Shopify account.</p>
    <p>If you haven't received a tracking email within 3 business days of placing your order, please <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--warm);">contact us</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping Page",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Shipping Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
